title: Zacks: Analysts Expect Q2 Holdings Inc (QTWO) Will Post Quarterly Sales of $58.34 Million
content: Analysts forecast that Q2 Holdings Inc (NYSE:QTWO) will post $58.34 million in sales for the current fiscal quarter, according to Zacks Investment Research. Seven analysts have issued estimates for Q2’s earnings, with the highest sales estimate coming in at $58.50 million and the lowest estimate coming in at $58.20 million. Q2 posted sales of $47.63 […]
